MetaDataPointOctetString.Description:
Lin network configuration (number of nodes, their type and their state)

structure : 
- {
    - enum configurationState (0 not initialized, 1 configurated, 255 not well configurated); 
    - UINT8 slave count (max 15); 
    - {
        - UINT8 nodeId; 
        - enum deviceType (ch pump, dhw pump ...);
        }
    }

Lin scheduling table with all the ids to send and their allocated time interval

structure : 
- {
    - UINT8 rows count (max 20); 
    - {
        - UINT8 frameId; 
        - UINT8 frameSlot high byte in ms; 
        - UINT8 frameSlot low byte in ms; 
        }
    }
